{"tid":377652,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"撇衞志豪開船P　阮兒「招親」曬燶心口","createTime":"2017-08-27T23:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T00:22:54.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55ab827fb7d64a61cecdb0644e32468608104565","tid":377652,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=419bfcf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阮兒嗌大家快啲去追佢呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=198555df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阮兒趁住夏天嘅尾巴約咗一班好友出海。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=98a030f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時唔少得晒三點式喇！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=a9b8078f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYeah！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=289d62a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有前面，當然有後面畀大家睇喇！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=7083cb80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚人靚景！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170827165145\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170827165145&h=f1a6aea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係呢張相喇！<br />\n<br />\n藝人阮兒形象性感，最近佢喺熱播中嘅無綫劇集《超時空男臣》中飾演集團高層「徐靜」，劇中仲「大解放」以性感打扮「色誘」何廣沛，令人留下深刻印象！日前佢就趁風和日麗，約埋成班朋友去遊船河，着上黑色三點式嘅佢大晒34C驕人上圍同均勻身材，企喺甲板上享受日光浴，仲擺出多個誘人甫士影相，十足專業模特兒！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>又怕曬又要玩</strong><br />\n<br />\n不過擁有健康膚色嘅阮兒當日忽視咗陽光嘅威力，唔小心曬燶「咪咪」，佢笑住話：「今年係第一次遊船河，諗住『立秋』之後冇咁熱，點知最後曬到好黑，返屋企發覺皮膚有啲燶，仲敏感甩皮。（曬燶心口？ ）哈哈，有少少！其實我又要玩、又怕曬，因為一曬好易黑。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同衞志豪了解吓</strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，講到樂壇校長譚詠麟早前喺社交網上載飯局相，發現阮兒同藝人衞志豪竟「離奇」同場，兩個人對腳仲黐得好埋，仲因為咁而傳出緋聞，問到衞志豪有冇同佢一齊遊船河？阮兒就甜笑話：「佢冇去，我哋係朋友咋，拍《同盟》時識嘅。（追你？）有追我，但未係一齊，了解吓先啦，之前嗰段感情太傷我心。」情傷中嘅阮兒仲搞笑咁公開「招親」，話希望識多幾個朋友先，佢話：「今次去船P就係想識多啲男仔朋友，我依家係單身，歡迎大家追我！」咁衞志豪咪會有好多勁敵？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170826%2Fbkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001.html&d=oSGnfBqN02MfYvGrMXtr1DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=01a6cf90\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170826/bkn-20170826231527868-0826_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f6c33acaf4567341a5ca6ebdb7dd823f57dc671f","tid":377652,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:22:16.000Z","msg":"呢隻雞邊撚個嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  141<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3170a7ba74e9f9d9e9be92dbe4eb7937a2f22a41","tid":377652,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:22:54.000Z","msg":"咁撚平比盡500"}]}